            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName key="#Placitum/iudicatum"><name ref="Gausfredus"
                                >Gausfrid</name></persName> una cum coniuge mea <persName
                            key="#Placitum/iudicatum"><name ref="Gausberga"
                            >Gausperga</name></persName>, abitatoribus in <placeName
                            ref="#places/1024">Vada</placeName>, quia ante hos annos per <rs
                            key="#Offersio/donatio">cartulam offersionis</rs> quondam <persName
                            key="#Offersio/donatio #Petiae"><name ref="Pretestatus"
                                >Praetestatus</name></persName> germanus meus, idest Gauspergae,
                        dedit <rs key="#Churches">ecclesiae</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/613">Sancti
                            Colombani</orgName> pro anima sua <rs key="#Petiae">terrulam</rs> quae
                        est iuxta <orgName key="#Mother_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/68">Sancti
                            Martini</orgName>. Pro hac re nos qui supra Gausfrid seu Gasperga vir et
                        coniux per hanc cartulam pro animae nostrae remedio tertiam portionem de
                        ipsa <rs key="#Petiae">terra</rs>, quam ego <rs key="#Placitum/iudicatum"
                            >per iudicium vici</rs> tecum uxor mea, offerre videmur Deo et tibi
                        praedictae <rs key="#Churches">ecclesiae</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/613">beati Sancti
                            Colombani</orgName> (â€¦). Actum <placeName ref="#places/4"
                            >Luca</placeName>. <foreign>Sottoscrizioni</foreign>: + Gausfridi; +
                        Gausperga; + <persName key="#Witness #Other_clerics"><name ref="Birrica"
                                >Birrica</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clericus</rs>; (ss) <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Tachipertus">Tachipertu</name></persName>; (ss) <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Willeradus">Willerad</name></persName>; (ss)
                            <persName key="#Witness" ref="#people/702">Sunderadu</persName>; (ss)
                            <persName key="#Witness" ref="#people/708">Perisundus</persName> filius
                        Sunderadi (ss). <foreign>Scrive</foreign>: <persName
                            key="#Writer #Other_clerics"><name ref="Ostribertus"
                            >Austripertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clericus</rs>.</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div type="bibliography" subtype="editions">
                        <p>MDL IV/1, n. 66 (ad an. 768); reg. MDL V/2, n. 109; CDL II, 221, pp.
                    256-257; ChLA, XXXIV, 1003.</p>
                    </div>
